Notice # 01-181

May 31, 2001


TO:

All NYMEX and COMEX Members and Member Firms


FROM:

Neal L. Wolkoff, Executive Vice President


RE:

Delisting of FTSE Eurotop 100 Option Contract


DATE:

May 31, 2001

===========================================================


Please be advised that the Exchange has determined to delist the FTSE Eurotop

100 Option contract. The delisting shall become effective on Friday, June 8,

2001.


If you have any questions concerning this change, please contact Jay

Gottlieb, Research Department, at (212) 299- 2607.


